Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.99,0:00:28.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我出門了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:28.99,0:00:34.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.01,0:00:56.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,遲到啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.02,0:00:59.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真糟糕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:59.99,0:01:04.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你又賴床了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:07.00,0:01:12.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.00,0:01:16.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等我幫你剝頭髮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:16.01,0:01:19.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來不及了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:16.01,0:01:21.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行你頭髮很亂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:22.01,0:01:27.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是慌張
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.00,0:05:16.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,（瑜伽教學）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.00,0:05:41.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是在幹嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.01,0:05:44.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,朋友來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.01,0:05:49.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.01,0:05:51.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請坐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.02,0:05:55.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打擾了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.99,0:06:01.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就能準備蛋糕嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.99,0:06:06.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,唉呀又不是女友來玩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.00,0:06:09.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用介意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.00,0:06:14.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我去準備茶點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.02,0:06:31.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好贊呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.99,0:06:33.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你媽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.99,0:06:35.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我媽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.99,0:06:39.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是你後母吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.00,0:06:43.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他是我媽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.00,0:06:46.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好年輕啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.00,0:06:51.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說什麼呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.01,0:06:59.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱歉沒啥好東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.02,0:07:01.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有關係的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.99,0:07:06.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,慢慢玩呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.99,0:07:11.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,留下來吃飯好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.50,0:07:16.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你喜歡什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.50,0:07:20.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.50,0:07:23.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.51,0:07:28.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,頭髮又亂了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.49,0:07:43.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你媽媽味道很棒呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.49,0:07:48.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哪有什麼味道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.50,0:07:54.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,腋下呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.54,0:07:59.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.51,0:08:37.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,同學呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.51,0:08:40.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.52,0:08:43.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,唉呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.52,0:08:47.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我還多買了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.49,0:08:52.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.50,0:09:00.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.50,0:09:05.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幫你按摩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.51,0:09:10.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,天塌下來羅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.51,0:09:15.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,忽然對我這麼好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.49,0:09:22.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不會多給零用錢喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.49,0:09:28.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.50,0:09:32.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是那邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.50,0:09:37.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,腋下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.51,0:09:44.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把手舉起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.51,0:09:46.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.52,0:09:51.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.49,0:09:59.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,繼續幫你彎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.50,0:10:12.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.51,0:10:19.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.52,0:10:23.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不舒服嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.52,0:10:28.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.49,0:10:34.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真不錯呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.50,0:10:42.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天菜好多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.51,0:10:46.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,本來要留他同學吃飯的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.51,0:10:51.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過回去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.51,0:10:54.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小建
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.52,0:10:59.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下次再叫他來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.50,0:11:18.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有冰的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.51,0:11:21.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幫我準備
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.51,0:11:25.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.51,0:11:28.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老是麻煩你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.52,0:11:31.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,唉呀今天不累嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.49,0:11:34.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小建剛剛幫我按了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.49,0:11:39.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他比你厲害喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.54,0:11:55.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.51,0:12:00.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是幹嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.52,0:12:04.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,維持就這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.49,0:12:09.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我愛這感覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.49,0:12:15.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真奇怪呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.50,0:12:21.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.50,0:12:26.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.51,0:12:33.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我還沒洗澡呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.52,0:12:38.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒差我喜歡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.50,0:12:51.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.50,0:12:56.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別這樣子啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.51,0:13:07.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這味道真好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.49,0:13:16.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.49,0:13:19.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那你就聞吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.50,0:13:21.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,會不會被看到呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.50,0:13:23.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我真擔心呢
