Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.51,0:14:14.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很爽不是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.51,0:14:44.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,短短的毛
